  "detailed_description": "My Best Nightmare is the Point & Click quest about the first day of work at a custom dream-making company, which very quickly turns into hell.<br><br>An adventure full of riddles, plot twists, and unusual locations. Get inside the head of a mentally ill man and find out what caused his ailment.<br><br>Find items and use them to advance further.<br><br>Read character dialogues and immerse yourself in a story with multiple endings.<br><br>Feel the unfriendliness of the world you find yourself in.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719000/extras/08c82fb320808e3396f6ad00ab51aba2.avif?t=1763663708\" width=698 height=482 /></span>",
